{"tid":1661681,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢發到冇晒錢既入黎!!","createTime":"2019-10-18T08:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T10:26:07.000Z","uid":18740,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"33a6532b628603195add486a9c5d12aba7924e27","tid":1661681,"uid":18740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T08:54:13.000Z","msg":"好多手足發夢買左好多野搞到唔夠洗，捐錢長遠幫唔到幾多，咁我就整合左少少資料俾學生哥睇，等大家可以發夢得黎唔會餓死，有經濟能力既可以岀返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>炒散 (餐廳/會展)</strong><br />\n我覺得無論男定女都好，做餐廳既炒散會易上手d， 一黎時間自己報，而且有d可以即日出糧， 有一張MPF就番得工，人工平均$55-$70/hour<br />\n<br />\n搵工就係google打炒散就有，有一間c字頭比較岀名既可以搵下<br />\n<br />\nMPF Link &gt; <a href=\"http://www.mpfa.org.hk/tchm/IS_AC/index.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfa.org.hk%2Ftchm%2FIS_AC%2Findex.jsp&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=0c9a0c7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mpfa.org.hk/tchm/IS_AC/index.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>地盤</em><br />\n呢一個人工比較高， 不過辛苦d， 做之前要上一日堂搞張平安卡，同埋工人註冊證，ｄ人通常加埋身分證叫三寶，白紙人工就平均$800+<br />\n<br />\n搵工就係Facebook d page就有，不過最好搵d大盤同即日岀糧安全d<br />\n<br />\n平安咭 &gt; <a href=\"http://www.hkmanpower.com/safety_card.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkmanpower.com%2Fsafety_card.php&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=1b8bf6b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkmanpower.com/safety_card.php</a><br />\n<br />\n工人註冊證&gt; <a href=\"http://www.cic.hk/chi/main/registration_services/construction_workers_regi/application/application_procedure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cic.hk%2Fchi%2Fmain%2Fregistration_services%2Fconstruction_workers_regi%2Fapplication%2Fapplication_procedure%2F&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=135574c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cic.hk/chi/main/registration_services/construction_workers_regi/application/application_procedure/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1821f998e4ee11e15df85bbdb8ceb8fc62d4ab64","tid":1661681,"uid":18740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T08:59:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3044c785b439e5d8d791d88fd7e36f875dcd5377","tid":1661681,"uid":159413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T10:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}